title: Rare Hits Of The 80's Vol. 71
description:
Here's another mix of weird underground end of music, the un-loved and 
unknown bands of the garage and wave generation. Punk and cast off rejects of 
our musical culture that make all the innovations and inroads and new kinds of music 
but get none of the glory or the money.
